title: Independent Candidate Zahid Ismail wins PP-270 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 10 (APP): Independent Candidate, Muhammad Zahid Ismail has won the Punjab Assembly election from PP-270, Muzaffargarh-III by securing 28,258 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Mian Imtiaz Aleem Qureshi of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) who bagged 24,531 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 52.53%.
